\c 9
\s Kutendeuka kwaSauro
\p
\v 1 Asi Sauro achiri kungofema kutyisa nokuponda akamirisana navadzidzi vaShe, wakaenda kumupristi mukuru,
\v 2 akakumbira kwaari magwaro oku\add enda\add* Dhamaseko kumasinagoge, kuti kana awana ani nani weNzira iyi, vangava varume kana vakadzi, auye navo Jerusarema vakasungwa.
\v 3 Zvino wakati ari parwendo akasvika pedo neDhamaseko, kamwe-kamwe kwakapenya kwakamupoteredza chiedza chakabva kudenga,
\v 4 akawira pasi, akanzwa inzwi richiti kwaari: Sauro, Sauro, unonditambudzireiko?
\v 5 Iye akati: Ndimwi aniko Ishe? Ishe akati: Ndini Jesu waunotambudza; zvinokuremera kukava zvinobaya.
\v 6 Iye achidedera nokushamiswa akati: Ishe, munoda kuti ndiiteiko? Ishe \add akati \add*kwaari: Simuka uende muguta, uchandoudzwa zvaunofanira kuita.
\v 7 Varume vaifamba naye vakamira vakashaya chokutaura, vachinzwa inzwi, asi vasingavoni munhu.
\v 8 Zvino Sauro akasimuka kubva pasi; asi wakati asvunudza meso ake, haana kuona munhu; vakamubata ruvoko, vakamuisa Dhamaseko.
\v 9 Akaita mazuva matatu asingavoni, asingadyi kana kunwa.
\v 10 Zvino pakanga panomumwe mudzidzi paDhamaseko, \add wainzi\add* Ananiasi nezita; Ishe akati kwaari muchiratidzo: Ananiasi! Iye akati: Tarirai ndini Ishe!
\v 11 Ishe \add akati\add* kwaari: Simuka, uende munzira yomuguta inonzi Yakarurama, ubvunze mumba maJudhasi, \add munhu\add* unonzi Sauro weTaso; nokuti tarira unonyengetera;
\v 12 naiye wavona muchiratidzo, murume unonzi Ananiasi achipinda, achiisa ruvoko pamusoro pake, kuti avonezve.
\v 13 Ipapo Ananiasi akapindura, \add akati\add*: Ishe, ndakanzwa navazhinji zvomunhu uyu, zvakakura sei zvakaipa zvaakaitira vatsvene venyu paJerusarema;
\v 14 napano unesimba kubva kuvapristi vakuru, kusunga vose vanodana zita renyu.
\v 15 Asi Ishe wakati kwaari: Enda, nokuti iye mudziyo wakasarudzwa kwandiri, kutakurira zita rangu kuvahedheni namadzimambo, navana vaIsraeri;
\v 16 nokuti ndichamuratidza kukura kwezvinhu zvaachafanira kutambura nokuda kwezita rangu.
\v 17 Ipapo Ananiasi akaenda akapinda mumba, ndokuisa mavoko ake pamusoro pake akati: Sauro hama, Ishe Jesu, wakaonekwa kwauri munzira yawakavuya nayo, wandituma, kuti uvonezve, nokuzadzwa noMweya Mutsvene.
\v 18 Pakarepo kukawa mumeso ake zvinhu zvinenge mafunurwa, akavonazve; akasimuka ndokubhabhatidzwa.
\v 19 Zvino wakati adya akasimbiswa Sauro akagara navadzidzi paDhamaseko mamwe mazuva.
\v 20 Pakarepo akaparidza Kristu mumasinagoge, kuti ndiye Mwanakomana waMwari.
\v 21 Asi vose vaka\add zvi\add*nzwa vakashamiswa vakati: Ko uyu haazi iye waiparadza avo vaidana kuzita iri paJerusarema here, akavuyira izvozvo pano, kuti aende navo vakasungwa kuvapristi vakuru?
\v 22 Asi Sauro wakaramba achisimbiswa, akavhiringidza vaJudha vakanga vagere Dhamaseko, achiratidza kuti uyu ndiye Kristu.
\s Sauro unodzingwa paDhamasko neJerusarema
\p
\v 23 Zvino mazuva mazhinji akati azadziswa, vaJudha vakarangana kumuvuraya.
\v 24 Asi zano ravo rakazikamwa naSauro. Vakarindavo masuvo masikati novusiku, kuti vamuvuraye.
\v 25 Zvino vadzidzi vakamutora vusiku, vaka\add mu\add*burusa naparusvingo vachi\add mu\add*burusa \add ari\add* mudengu.
\v 26 Zvino Sauro wakati asvika Jerusarema, akaidza kuzvibatanidza kuvadzidzi; asi vose vaimutya vasingatendi kuti \add wava\add* mudzidzi.
\v 27 Zvino Bhanabhasi wakamutora, akauya \add naye\add* kuvaapositori, ndokurondedzera kwavari kuti wakavona Ishe sei munzira, uye kuti wakanga ataura naye, uye kuti wakaparidza sei asingatyi paDhamaseko muzita raJesu.
\v 28 Akagara navo achipinda nokubuda paJerusarema,
\v 29 akataura asingatyi muzita raShe Jesu. Akapikisa vaHerenisiti*; asi ivo vakaidza kumuvuraya.
\v 30 Zvino hama dzakati dzichi\add zvi\add*ziva dzikamuburusira Kesariya, ndokumutumira Taso.
\v 31 Zvino kereke paJudhiya yose neGariri, neSamaria, ikava norugare, ikasimbiswa, ikawedzerwa, ichifamba ichitya Ishe, ichinyaradzwa noMweya Mutsvene.
\s Kuporeswa kwaEneasi
\p
\v 32 Zvino zvakaitika apo Peturo achipota kose, akaburukiravo kuvatsvene vakanga vagere Ridha.
\v 33 Akawanapo mumwe munhu wainzi Eneasi, wakanga avete panhovo yake makore masere, akawoma mitezo.
\v 34 Peturo akati kwaari: Eneasi, Jesu Kristu unokuporesa; simuka, uzviwarurire. Akasimuka pakarepo.
\v 35 Zvino vose vakanga vagere Ridha neSaroni vakamuvona, vakatendevukira kunaShe.
\s Kumutswa kwaTabhita parufu
\p
\v 36 Zvino paivapo paJopa mumwe mudzidzikadzi \add wainzi\add* Tabhita nezita, ndokuti Dorkasi, kana zvichishandurwa. Mukadzi uyu wakashingaira zvikuru pamabasa akanaka nezvipo zvaaiita.
\v 37 Zvino zvakaitika namazuva iwayo kuti iye akarwara ndokufa. Vakati vamushambidza, vakamuisa muimba yokumusoro,
\v 38 Zvino Ridha zvayakanga iri pedo neJopa, vadzidzi vakati vanzwa kuti Peturo wakanga aripo, vakatumira kwaari varume vaviri, vachikumbira zvikuru kuti asanonoka kuuya kwavari.
\v 39 Ipapo Peturo akasimuka akaenda navo. Wakati asvika vakamuisa kuimba yokumusoro, chirikadzi dzose dzikamira naye dzichichema, vachiratidza zvokupfeka nenguvo, dzakanga dzaitwa naDorkasi, achiri navo.
\v 40 Zvino Peturo akavabudisira panze vose, akafugama pasi, akanyengetera, ndokutendevukira kumutumbi, akati: Tabhita, muka! Akasvunura meso ake; zvino wakati achivona Peturo, akagara.
\v 41 Akamutendekera ruvoko, akamusimudza; akati adana vatsvene nechirikadzi, akamukumikidza ari mupenyu.
\v 42 Zvikazikamwa paJopa yose; vazhinji vakatenda munaShe.
\v 43 Zvakaitika kuti wakagara mazuva mazhinji paJopa, nomumwe Simoni musuki wamatehwe.
